text: The Shaman fringe-limbed tree frog (Ecnomiohyla sukia) is a frog that lives in Costa Rica. Scientists have seen it in two places, between 400 and 1000 meters above sea level. This frog has more webbing on its feet than other frogs in Ecnomiohyla. ==References== Category:Frogs of North America
title: Ecnomiohyla sukia
